mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SPECIAL FEATURES "The Preliminary Language of Square Dancing", "What is "High Level?"". "What's On Your Mind?", and "Springfield Mountain, or The Pesky Sarpint". This edition also includes the the regular features entitled "Square Dance Date Book", "From the Floor", "As I See It", "What Are They Wearing?", "Ladies on the Square: Tricks 'n' Trims", "Style Series: Visualizing a Dance", "Chuck Jones' Note Book", "The Square Dance Picture", "Round the Outside Ring", "Caller of the Month: George Watts", "Paging the Roundancers: Fred and Georgie Bunker", and "On the Record".
